PW Sports Wagering -- Authorize Sports Wagering Activities - Act 215, 2020
Race.SummaryText: PROPOSITION TO AUTHORIZE SPORTS WAGERING ACTIVITIES.
Race.FullText: Shall sports wagering activities and operations be permitted in the parish of Franklin?

Race.SpecificTitle: PW Proposition No. 1 of 3 -- 4.07 Mills Renewal - PJ - 5 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Parish of Franklin, State of Louisiana (the "Parish"), levy a four and seven hundredths (4.07) mills tax on all property subject to taxation in the Parish (an estimated $436,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of five (5) years, beginning with the year 2023 and ending with the year 2027, for the purpose of operation and maintenance of the Parish Courthouse?

Race.SpecificTitle: PW Proposition No. 2 of 3 -- 11.17 Mills Renewal - PJ - 5 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Parish of Franklin, State of Louisiana (the "Parish"), levy an eleven and seventeen hundredths (11.17) mills tax on all property subject to taxation in the Parish (an estimated $1,196,589 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of five (5) years, beginning with the year 2023 and ending with the year 2027, for the purpose of construction, maintenance and operation of, and the purchase of equipment for, the drainage system in the Parish?

Race.SpecificTitle: PW Proposition No. 3 of 3 -- 8.12 Mills Renewal - PJ - 5 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Parish of Franklin, State of Louisiana (the "Parish"), levy an eight and twelve hundredths (8.12) mills tax on all property subject to taxation in the Parish (an estimated $869,857 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of five (5) years, beginning with the year 2023 and ending with the year 2027, for the purpose of maintaining, operating and purchasing Parish equipment?
